Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: zope.app.principalannotation
Version: 3.5.0
Summary: Annotations for Zope Principals
Home-page: http://pypi.python.org/pypi/zope.app.principalannotation
Author: Zope Corporation and Contributors
Author-email: zope-dev@zope.org
License: ZPL 2.1
Description: This package implements annotation for Zope publisher principals. Common
        annotation techniques cannot be applied to principals, since they are created
        on the fly for every request.
        
        
        =======
        CHANGES
        =======
        
        3.5.0 (2009-02-01)
        ------------------
        
        - Move boostrap subscriber to bootstrap.zcml file and browser
        menu item definition to browser.zcml file to ease overriding
        and excluding configuration.
        - Use zope.container instead of zope.app.container.
        
        3.4.0 (2007-10-26)
        ------------------
        
        - Initial release independent of the main Zope tree.
        
